# ============================================================
# 第三方素材（license 禁止重新分发）
# Unity Asset Store 购买素材：保留本地，需要时各自从 Asset Store 下载
# ============================================================
art/environments/pixel-art-top-down-basic/
art/environments/pixel-art-top-down/
Assets/Art/Tilesets/pixel-art-top-down/
Assets/Art/Tilesets/pixel-art-top-down.meta
*.unitypackage
# 音效原包：Kenney=CC0 可分发，但 Leohpaz 免费包禁止再分发原包 → 原始 zip + 解压全集不入库
audio/_zips/

# 本地工具包 / 大模型二进制：可重新下载，不进库
tools/realesrgan/

# VFX 切帧质检输出：contact sheet / preview gif / debug check，不是生产资产
art/vfx/_contact_*.png
art/vfx/_preview_*.gif
art/vfx/_check_*.png
art/vfx/_gen/_contact_*.png
art/vfx/_gen/_preview_*.gif
art/vfx/_gen/_montage*.png

# ============================================================
# 草稿/待定美术（本地保留，不入库）
# ============================================================
art_undecided/
art_undecided.meta

# ============================================================
# .NET / VSCode C# 工具链本地缓存
# ============================================================
dotnet/

# ============================================================
# PixelLab 角色 ZIP（可随时由 character_id 重新下载，体积大且每次生成都会变）
# ============================================================
art/characters/*/character.zip
# raw PixelLab downloads (zip + extracted); re-downloadable from character_id
pixellab/characters/*/download/
# PixelLab review artifacts (filmstrip / contact sheet / preview gifs / ad-hoc
# compare images — all regenerable, underscore-prefixed, not shipped assets)
pixellab/characters/*/_preview/
pixellab/characters/*/_*.png
pixellab/characters/*/rotations/_*.png
# one-off temp scripts
scripts/_tmp_*.py
